token_info.name: Matrix Rain #OBJKT4OBJKT
token_info.description: This is a Matrix-like code raining effect using OBJKT4OBJKT characters set, built with JavaScript and the p5.js library, and based on the Coding Train guest Video tutorial by Emily Xie - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=S1TQCi9axzg  It has been created as my little contribution to the amazing #objkt4objkt initiative.  Thanks to Daniel Shiffman and Emily Xie for the great learning content.
